  <Question>
      <QuestionIdentifier>first_intruction</QuestionIdentifier>
      <DisplayName>Q1</DisplayName>
      <IsRequired>true</IsRequired>
      <QuestionContent>
          <FormattedContent><![CDATA[
                <p>
                Would you please help us build what is instructed in the given instruction set in 45 seconds? 
                Imagine you are playing a creative game in a 3-D voxel world, and you have unlimited access to blocks of certain kinds. 
                You will be instructed to follow verbatim (written in plain text) and are required to build things as instructed. 
                You have 45 seconds to complete the task.
                You would need use <b>'w/a/s/d'</b> to move <b>'forward/left/back/right'</b>,
                <b>'space'</b> to jump, <b>'double space'</b> to fly, <b>'shift'</b> to return to earch after flying
                and <b>'esc'</b> to leave the world and back to the website.
                </p>
                <h3> That is how the Builder should look in action:</h3> 
                <img src="https://iglumturkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/qualification-test/demo.gif" alt="Builder demo"/>
                <h3> Please note that you will only get paid if you: </h3>
                <ul>
                   <li>Click on "Submit" button at the bottom.</li>
                </ul> 
                <p>If an Architect has given the following instruction:</p>
                <i> Place a one green block </i>  
          ]]></FormattedContent>
    <Text>Using the radio button, pick which picture reflects the structure you would have built following the Architect's instruction?</Text>
      </QuestionContent>
      <AnswerSpecification>
        <SelectionAnswer>
          <StyleSuggestion>radiobutton</StyleSuggestion>
          <Selections>
            <Selection>
              <SelectionIdentifier>right</SelectionIdentifier>
                <Binary>
                  <MimeType>
                  <Type>image</Type>
                  <SubType>png</SubType>
                  </MimeType>
                <DataURL>https://iglumturkstorage.blob.core.windows.net/qualification-test/iglu-one-green-block.png</DataURL>
                <AltText></AltText>
                </Binary>
            </Selection>
            <Selection>
              <SelectionIdentifier>wrong1</SelectionIdentifier>
                <Binary>
                  <MimeType>
